**Professional Profile**
Nguyễn Hà My is an aspiring Software Developer with extensive hands-on project experience across web, mobile, and cross-platform development. Through multiple personal projects, My has demonstrated proficiency in building robust applications, including a mobile English learning app, an e-commerce platform, and web-based inventory and student management systems. Key contributions include implementing clean architecture, secure authentication, real-time data integration, and intuitive user interfaces, showcasing practical skills in full-stack development.

**Core Skills & Technology**
Proficient in a diverse range of technologies including Java, Python, Dart, JavaScript, Flutter, ReactJS, Node.js, MongoDB, Firebase, RESTful API, Git, and Tailwind CSS.

**Education & Certifications**
Currently pursuing a Bachelor's degree in Information Technology - Software Engineering at Ton Duc Thang University, with an anticipated graduation in 2026. My is also certified in Agile Development & Scrum Framework and holds an English APTIS Level B1 (CEFR) certification.